longBusinessSummary: Digatrade Financial Corp. operates as a financial technology services company. It focuses on offering research and development related services in the digital-asset industry for prospective institutional customers. The company was formerly known as Bit-X Financial Corporation and changed its name to Digatrade Financial Corp. in October 2015. Digatrade Financial Corp. was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
